All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class Clock
extends HardwareFeature

Objects of this class represent a clock as specified by PKCS#11 v2.11. Remind that this is a snapshot; this means that this object does not get the values from the token on demand it gets them uppon instanciation.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Karl Scheibelhofer
